WEBVTT

00:00:00.730 --> 00:00:03.424
What's the worst that could happen?

00:00:04.336 --> 00:00:06.558
Almost exactly 10 years ago,

00:00:06.582 --> 00:00:10.307
I was sitting in an exam room
that was way too cold

00:00:10.331 --> 00:00:12.828
waiting to meet my new oncologist.

00:00:12.852 --> 00:00:14.787
I was terrified.

00:00:14.811 --> 00:00:18.788
Even though my partner at the time
was sitting right by my side,

00:00:18.812 --> 00:00:20.787
I felt completely alone.

00:00:21.298 --> 00:00:24.284
I had just been diagnosed
with breast cancer,

00:00:24.308 --> 00:00:25.934
and it seemed at the time

00:00:25.958 --> 00:00:30.131
that a single bright spot
on a scan of my right lung